{"tid":399813,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"(有GIF有透)仆你個街,睇左蝴蝶效應,以為科幻片,點知係玄幻片","createTime":"2017-09-14T09:29:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T13:59:47.000Z","uid":49391,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"18673aab563a5b08bc3d5f429db75285b9af5d5c","tid":399813,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T09:29:19.000Z","msg":"男主角真係畀佢果班仆街損友害得好撚慘呀,屌你老母<br />\n試左穿梭幾次,乜都夠皮啦<br />\n畀著我就乾脆咪撚理班仆街,用能力令自己有權有勢,富甲一方就算<br />\n為左班仆街梭乎,自己去死,值得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6cd46489c8bfc4146578e3ff19300d38f7f4b48","tid":399813,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T09:31:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/DLQRz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FDLQRz.gif&h=0512565f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好似係拍緊羅賓漢同瑪麗安的愛情故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/DLLtp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FDLLtp.gif&h=b769bbe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n老虎唔發威你當我病貓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0f2e63baeaafaf376a109d9b50542fc07f21b55","tid":399813,"uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T09:35:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/DLwsb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FDLwsb.gif&h=7d8599b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 肥仔之後就性情大變<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://i.imag.cx/DLcQP.gif\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FDLcQP.gif&d=XGngVn4aDIsJXW9MQz%2Bu2J4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=9e9f85dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://i.imag.cx/DLcQP.gif</a><br />\n裸女入鏡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30af8bd54e81e7e767282bb8799f52107515f75f","tid":399813,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T09:37:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imag.cx/DLxK6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imag.cx%2FDLxK6.gif&h=c80b5dcd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n請你食吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最幫得手反而係一個宗教狂熱的耶撚獄友,世事真係講唔埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957cea4f47f8b1c8bf10897697d23aad7c3b840f","tid":399813,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T09:40:12.000Z","msg":"原來有成4個結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以整個唔理班仆街,自己發大達的結局<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n劇場版結局：伊万做了最後一次時空穿梭，改變自己的歷史，最後與本來是他愛人的凱麗在茫茫人海里相遇，卻只是相互一瞥，而後擦肩而過。<br />\n <br />\n結局2：由劇場版派生的結局，伊万和凱麗在茫茫人海中相遇，伊万請她喝咖啡。<br />\n <br />\n結局3（開放式結局）：同樣由劇場版派生的結局，伊万和凱麗在茫茫人海中相遇，返身追她而去。<br />\n <br />\n導演剪輯版結局：伊万看著母親懷著他時的家庭錄像，記憶帶他回到了母體重新成為胎兒，由於相信他的存在會毀滅周圍的一切，他掙扎著用母親的臍帶把自己勒死了。<br />\n<br />\n解讀：本片導演埃里克&middot;布雷斯原本只拍了導演剪輯版的結局，但發行方新線影業擔心這個結尾太過離奇和灰暗，容易引起負面輿論，因而讓導演拍攝了後續幾個結尾，包括如今的劇場版結尾。幾個結局中導演最不喜歡結局2，這不但是最俗套的好萊塢路子，也違背了電影的主題，即人類無法去改變過往的歷史。"},{"pid":"41d794ce0b5e290a368c8345bb762ba138550300","tid":399813,"uid":34080,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T09:42:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0e50cc63dad0ea6a452745c7cf2255425dc2a350","tid":399813,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T09:44:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"297c9baf623784d8487c2d841d26e3163b57fd76","tid":399813,"uid":53259,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-14T09:44:15.000Z","msg":"老了老了<br />\n依家D細路都開始大了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cl